# Local stale build artifacts — server/ui-dist gets generated on the host
# during dev/test (e.g. when running the UI build with `--outDir
# ../server/ui-dist`). If it sneaks into `COPY . .` it shadows the freshly
# built ui/dist because server/src/app.ts checks `../ui-dist` first.
server/ui-dist
